---
import LandingLayout from "../layouts/LandingLayout.astro";
import LandingHeader from "../components/LandingHeader.astro";
---
<LandingLayout>
  <LandingHeader />
  <section class="w-full max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center flex-1 text-base-content py-8">
    <article class="leading-relaxed">
      <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold">Welcome to DETECT</h1>
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold mt-4">AI-Powered Lie Detection Through Eye Movement Analysis</h2>
      <p class="mt-6">
        DETECT is an advanced deception detection system that leverages <strong>statistical deterministic modeling</strong> to analyze <strong>eye movement patterns</strong>. By examining gaze shifts, fixation points, and pupil motion, DETECT identifies behavioral inconsistencies that may indicate deception.
      </p>
      <hr class="my-6 border-t border-base-content"/>
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold mt-6">How DETECT Works</h2>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-4">1Ô∏è‚É£ Start on the Landing Page</h3>
      <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside">
        <li>New users can <strong>sign up</strong> for an account.</li>
        <li>Registered users can <strong>log in</strong> to access DETECT's dashboard.</li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-4">2Ô∏è‚É£ Secure User Authentication</h3>
      <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside">
        <li>If a user forgets their password, they can <strong>reset it</strong> through the recovery system.</li>
        <li>The system <strong>authenticates credentials</strong> before granting access.</li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-4">3Ô∏è‚É£ Access the User Dashboard</h3>
      <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Once logged in, users land on the <strong>dashboard</strong>, where they can choose how to proceed.</li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-4">4Ô∏è‚É£ Choose an Analysis Method</h3>
      <p class="mt-2">Users have <strong>three main options</strong> for lie detection:</p>
      <ol class="mt-2 list-decimal list-inside">
        <li><strong>Upload a Video</strong> ‚Äì Analyze deception indicators in a pre-recorded video.</li>
        <li><strong>Live Webcam Analysis</strong> ‚Äì Run real-time deception detection using the user‚Äôs webcam.</li>
        <li><strong>View Prior Metrics</strong> ‚Äì Review past analysis results for comparative study.</li>
      </ol>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-4">5Ô∏è‚É£ Processing &amp; Results</h3>
      <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside">
        <li>For <strong>videos</strong> and <strong>live sessions</strong>, DETECT processes <strong>eye movement patterns</strong> to detect inconsistencies.</li>
        <li>Results are displayed in the <strong>metrics panel</strong>, allowing users to assess deception likelihood.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-6">
        üîí <strong>Privacy &amp; Security</strong> ‚Äì All analysis is performed in real time without storing personal data.
      </p>
      <hr class="my-6 border-t border-base-content"/>
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold mt-6">Who Can Use DETECT?</h2>
      <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside">
        <li>‚úî <strong>Law Enforcement &amp; Investigators</strong> ‚Äì Assess potential deception during interrogations or screenings.</li>
        <li>‚úî <strong>Corporate Security &amp; Hiring</strong> ‚Äì Enhance background checks and fraud detection.</li>
        <li>‚úî <strong>Academic &amp; Psychological Research</strong> ‚Äì Study cognitive load and deception patterns through eye-tracking data.</li>
        <li>‚úî <strong>Media &amp; Journalism</strong> ‚Äì Evaluate interviewee behavior for signs of misinformation.</li>
        <li>‚úî <strong>Personal Use &amp; Curiosity</strong> ‚Äì Explore how deception correlates with gaze behavior.</li>
      </ul>
      <hr class="my-6 border-t border-base-content"/>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">Start Using DETECT Today!</h3>
      <p class="mt-2">
        Ready to explore the future of AI-powered deception detection? <strong>Sign up now and experience DETECT firsthand.</strong>
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4">
        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-outline starfunk">Login</a>
        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-outline starfunk hidden md:inline-block">Sign Up</a>
      </p>
      <p class="mt-6">
        üî¨ <strong>Developed by AAI Solution</strong> | A Senior Design Project at UCF
      </p>
      <!-- Images container: Side padding removed -->
      <div class="flex w-full gap-4 mt-8">
        <img src="/images/001.jpg" alt="Image 001" class="w-1/2 object-cover" />
        <img src="/images/002.jpg" alt="Image 002" class="w-1/2 object-cover" />
      </div>
    </article>
